Class EigPreconditioner

    public class EigPreconditioner
extends Operator
    SPARSE-EIG Java EigPreconditioner class.

    SPARSE-EIG uses the MTJ Java library (matrix-toolkits-java) and Netlib Java (netlib-java) for numerical linear algebra and matrix computations.

    This class provides the setup for the solver and TMJ preconditioning

    Author:
    Rico Argentati
